subject: Your beneficiary fund worth's
body:
Your beneficiary fund worth's sum of $9.7Million has been in our
custody and you would have received it for long. Are you really ready
to receive this fund?
Remember since when i kept telling you this, to avoid losing your fund.

subject: Re: Your beneficiary fund worth's
body:
Dear Sir/Madam,

I am not aware of any funds being held in my name. Could you please provide more details about this? How did the fund come into your custody and why has it been held for so long?

Best wishes,
Vernon
